sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_048_4_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Reservation of a Connector - Rejected
    Note over CP,CS: Table 171, page 146 (CompliancyTestTool-TestCaseDocument)
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>reservationId: <unique id><br/>expiryDate: <future timestamp>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Rejected)
    Note over CP: CP-side validation:<br/>status must be Rejected
    Note over CS: CS-side validation:<br/>connectorId = Configured ConnectorId<br/>idTag = Configured Valid IdTag

    Note over CP,CS: Expected: Central System accepts the non-Accepted reservation status
